<h4 >2017</h4>


<li>"<a href="http://online.liebertpub.com/doi/abs/10.1089/elj.2017.0452">Partisan Gerrymandering and the Political Process: Effects on Roll-Call Voting and State Policies</a>." <i>Election Law Journal</i>. December, 2017. 16(4): 453-469. (with <a href='http://caughey.mit.edu/welcome'  class="coauthor" target="_blank">Devin Caughey</a> and <a href='http://www.polisci.ucla.edu/people/chris-tausanovitch'  class="coauthor" target="_blank">Chris Tausanovitch</a>) 
